data.description: WOW!! Are you looking for a newer construction home?  Here is is!! 3BR/2BA split plan.  Walk in and you will notice how open the floor plan is.  The perfect home for entertaining.  Large living room that overlooks the large kitchen with granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances and loads of cabinets with a pantry.  Master is very large with a large walk-in closet and huge bathroom with a beautiful shower.  There is a utility closet with tankless hot water heater.  On the other side of the house are 2 large bedrooms and a beautiful bathroom.  There is a small patio outside also.  Roof, AC, all appliances are 3 years old!! Located in a Non-Evac Zone.  Hurry on this one!
